column4:
Working together &amp; across the aisle is how you get things done in the Senate. I teamed up w/
@SenatorFischer to help make sure all Americans can access mental health services, especially during
#COVID19. Read abt our bipartisan bill in our @rollcall op-ed: https://t.co/Gq5HPz34jX

UPDATE: just yesterday, researchers presented a new report on how serious the maternal mortality crisis is for rural areas.

@StarTribune has the story and it’s just devastating. We need to ensure mothers everywhere can access high quality health care.

https://t.co/LzRJDt4dYm https://t.co/ct8wnFCZTp
